messages.speech:
Headache is a  painful sensation in any part of the head that can be a sign of stress or emotional distress that may occur with other symptoms. Here are some tips for Headache Relief:
1. Close your eyes and rest.
2. Massage your neck and temples.
3. Warm-up your neck.
4. Try putting a heating pad or a warm cloth around your neck and the base skull to ease tension headaches.
5. Minimize Stress.
